{"name": "rosetta-soil", "metadata": {"name": "rosetta-soil", "version": "0.1.2", "classifiers": ["Intended Audience :: Science/Research", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU General Public License v2 or later (GPLv2+)", "Topic :: Scientific/Engineering"], "home_page": "https://github.com/usda-ars-ussl/rosetta-soil", "license": "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU General Public License v2 or later (GPLv2+)", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["numpy"], "summary": "Predict soil hydraulic parameters from basic characterization data.", "upload_time": 1714695613}, "documentation": ["Implementation of the Rosetta pedotransfer function model. Rosetta predicts parameters for the van Genuchten unsaturated soil hydraulic properties model, using as input basic soil characterization data such bulk density and percentages of sand, silt, and clay.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "rosetta.__version__", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "rosetta.__version__.__version__", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "rosetta.rosetta", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "rosetta.rosetta.to_floats", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "seq", "type": {"name": "Sequence", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Sequence", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "List", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.List", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "float", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.float", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "rosetta.rosetta.rosetta", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "rosetta_version", "type": {"name": "int", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.int", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "soildata", "type": {"name": "SoilData", "xref": {"fqname": "rosetta.rosetta.SoilData", "project": null}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "Tuple", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Tuple", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "Array2D", "xref": {"fqname": "Array2D", "project": null}, "params": null}, {"name": "Array2D", "xref": {"fqname": "Array2D", "project": null}, "params": null}, {"name": "Array1D", "xref": {"fqname": "Array1D", "project": null}, "params": null}]}, "documentation": ["Predict soil hydraulic parameters from soil characterization data.\n\nParameters\n----------\nrosetta_version : {1, 2, 3}\n\nsoildata : :class:`~rosetta.rosetta.SoilData`\n    List of soil characterization data, one entry per soil\n\nReturns\n-------\n(mean, stdev, codes)\n\nmean : 2D np.array, dtype=float\n    \n    ith row holds predicted soil hydraulic parameters for ith entry\n    in `soildata`.\n\n    array  |\n    column | parameter\n    -----------------\n       0   | theta_r, residual water content\n       1   | theta_s, saturated water content\n       2   | log10(alpha), van Genuchten 'alpha' parameter (1/cm)\n       3   | log10(npar), van Genuchten 'n' parameter\n       4   | log10(Ksat), saturated hydraulic conductivity (cm/day)\n\nstdev: 2D np.array, dtype=float\n\n    Standard deviations for parameters in `mean`.\n\ncodes : 1D np.array, dtype=int\n\n    ith entry is a code indicating the neural network model and\n    input data used to predict the ith row of `mean` and `stdev`.\n\n     code | data used\n    ---------------\n       2  | sand, silt, clay (SSC)\n       3  | SSC + bulk density (BD)\n       4  | SSC + BD + field capacity water content (TH33)\n       5  | SSC + BD + TH33 + wilting point water content (TH1500))\n      -1  | no result returned, insufficient or erroneous data\n\nExample\n-------\n>>> from rosetta import rosetta, SoilData\n\n# required ordering for data records:\n# [sa (%), si (%), cl (%), bd (g/cm3), th33, th1500]\n\n# sa, si, and cl are required; others optional\n\n>>> data = [\n        [30,30,40,1.5,0.3,0.1],  \n        [20,60,20],\n        [55,25,20,1.1]\n    ]\n\n>>> mean, stdev, codes = rosetta(3, SoilData.from_array(data))\n\n>>> print(mean)\n[[ 0.06872133  0.38390509 -2.45296887  0.17827395  0.98272273]\n[ 0.08994502  0.43013665 -2.42623575  0.17568733  1.19273113]\n[ 0.09130753  0.48503196 -2.02238809  0.15107161  1.90601478]]\n\n>>> print(stdev)\n[[ 0.01362899 0.01496918 0.12948704 0.03477392 0.17477977]\n[ 0.00670759 0.00878582 0.07413139 0.01323068 0.08709446]\n[ 0.01277141 0.01306217 0.10020312 0.01763982 0.14163567]]\n\n>>> print(codes)\n[5 2 3]"]}], "variables": [{"name": "rosetta.rosetta.Array1D", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "rosetta.rosetta.Array2D", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "rosetta.rosetta.ROSETTA_VERSIONS", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "rosetta.rosetta.ROSETTA_MODEL_CODES", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "rosetta.rosetta.ROSE2_COEFFICIENTS", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "rosetta.rosetta.RosettaError", "bases": ["Exception"], "methods": [{"name": "rosetta.rosetta.RosettaError.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "message", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}, {"name": "rosetta.rosetta.SoilDatum", "bases": ["NamedTuple"], "methods": [{"name": "rosetta.rosetta.SoilDatum.is_valid_separates", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "rosetta.rosetta.SoilDatum.is_valid_bulkdensity", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "rosetta.rosetta.SoilDatum.is_valid_fieldcap", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], 